The National Weather Service in Riverton has issued a Red Flag Warning, which is in effect from 1 PM to 7 PM MDT Wednesday. the Fire Weather Watch is no longer in effect. * IMPACTS: Low Humidities and Strong Gusty Winds will create erratic fire behavior.
